<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title><%= status %> 오류</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .btn {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .debug {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
            max-width: 500px;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="code"><%= status %></div>
<div class="message">
    <% if (404 === status) { %>
        요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.
    <% } else if (500 === status) { %>
        서버에 문제가 발생했습니다.
    <% } else { %>
        오류가 발생했습니다.
    <% } %>
</div>
<a class="btn" href="/v1/service/calendar">홈으로 돌아가기</a>

<% if (process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development' && message) { %>
    <div class="debug"><%= message %></div>
<% } %>
</body>
</html>